attachment/go4/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/go4.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Produk flagship GoPro saat ini. Sumber gambar: steves-digicams.com\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Produk flagship GoPro saat ini. Sumber gambar: steves-digicams.com&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/go4-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/go4.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-43560\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/go4.jpg\" alt=\"Produk flagship GoPro saat ini. Sumber gambar: steves-digicams.com\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/go4.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/go4-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-43560\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Produk flagship GoPro saat ini. Sumber gambar: steves-digicams.com</p></div>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">GoPro juga sempat “bermain-main” dengan bisnis ’<a href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/trend-drone-quadcopter-mainan-mahal-yang-prestisius-ada-lomba-balapannya-loh/\">consumer drone</a>’ walau akhirnya mundur teratur dari situ. GoPro Karma Drone diluncurkan bulan Oktober 2016. Di bulan berikutnya GoPro melakukan recall product alias penarikan produk dari pasaran karena masalah baterai. Laporan yang ada menyebutkan kalau GoPro Karma, yang dijual seharga $799 itu, bisa mendadak kehilangan sumber arus dari baterai dan menyebabkan drone itu jatuh karena tidak bertenaga. Perusahaan kemudian mengumumkan kalau Karma sudah beres dari masalah dan beredar kembali di toko-toko sejak Februari 2017. Tapi sepertinya reputasi dan kepercayaan publik pada produk ini sudah menurun (dan bahkan hilang), sehingga di bulan Januari 2018 kemarin GoPro mengumumkan kalau mereka melakukan diskontinyu produk pada GoPro Karma dan keluar/berhenti dari bisnis drone.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_43559\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-43559\" data-attachment-id=\"43559\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/gopro-hampir-bangkrut-zero-hero-back-zero/attachment/go3/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/go3.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"GoPro Karma drone. Sumber gambar: discoverglobal.co.uk\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;GoPro Karma drone. Sumber gambar: discoverglobal.co.uk&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/go3-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/go3.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-43559\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/go3.jpg\" alt=\"GoPro Karma drone. Sumber gambar: discoverglobal.co.ukGoPro Karma drone. Sumber gambar: discoverglobal.co.uk\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/go3.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/go3-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-43559\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">GoPro Karma drone. Sumber gambar: discoverglobal.co.uk</p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_43564\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-43564\" data-attachment-id=\"43564\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/gopro-hampir-bangkrut-zero-hero-back-zero/attachment/go8/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/go8.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"GoPro Karma drone terlihat keren saat mengudara. Sumber gambar: gopro.com\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;GoPro Karma drone terlihat keren saat mengudara. Sumber gambar: gopro.com&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/go8-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/go8.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-43564\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/go8.jpg\" alt=\"GoPro Karma drone terlihat keren saat mengudara. Sumber gambar: gopro.com\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/go8.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/go8-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-43564\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">GoPro Karma drone terlihat keren saat mengudara. Sumber gambar: gopro.com</p></div>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Masalah tidak hanya datang dari drone Karma untuk GoPro.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nilai saham mereka terus melorot jatuh, selaras dengan performa perusahaan yang makin turun. Margin keuntungan juga mengalami masalah serius. Bahkan mereka sampai perlu melakukan restrukturisasi. Tidak hanya di bagian proyeksi keuntungan, namun juga di jumlah pegawai dan harga retail produk mereka. PHK bertahap terus menghantui manajemen dan karyawan GoPro. Sekitar 20% dari jumlah karyawan sudah mengalami PHK dan ini belum menjamin karyawan yang lain akan selamat. Nick Woodman, founder &amp; CEO GoPro, Inc. dalam sebuah wawancara terbaru mengatakan kalau dia terbuka pada opsi bekerja sama dengan seseorang/perusahaan lain atau malah membeli perusahaannya sekalian.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_43558\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-43558\" data-attachment-id=\"43558\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/gopro-hampir-bangkrut-zero-hero-back-zero/attachment/go2/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/go2.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Produk mereka bagus. Tapi penjualannya terus menurun. Sumber gambar: detik.com\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Produk mereka bagus. Tapi penjualannya terus menurun. Sumber gambar: detik.com&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/go2-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/go2.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-43558\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/go2.jpg\" alt=\"Produk mereka bagus. Tapi penjualannya terus menurun. Sumber gambar: detik.com\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/go2.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/go2-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-43558\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Produk mereka bagus. Tapi penjualannya terus menurun. Sumber gambar: detik.com</p></div>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Menurut analisa yang ada, masalah GoPro bukan (hanya) di harga retail mereka yang tergolong tinggi. Kamera flagship mereka, GoPro Hero 6 Black, kini dijual dengan harga $399 setelah sebelumnya di $499. Salah satu “masalah” mereka ada di kualitas. Action camera mereka terlalu bagus. Terlalu bagus sehingga orang malas melakukan upgrade. Pemilik GoPro Hero 4 melihat GoPro Hero 5 hampir tidak ada bedanya sehingga mereka tetap memakai Go</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_43562\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-43562\" data-attachment-id=\"43562\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/gopro-hampir-bangkrut-zero-hero-back-zero/attachment/go6/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/go6.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Spek yang tidak terlalu jauh. Sumber gambar: phandroid.com\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Spek yang tidak terlalu jauh. Sumber gambar: phandroid.com&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/go6-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/go6.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-43562\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/go6.jpg\" alt=\"Spek yang tidak terlalu jauh. Sumber gambar: phandroid.com\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/go6.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/go6-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-43562\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Spek yang tidak terlalu jauh. Sumber gambar: phandroid.com</p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_43561\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-43561\" data-attachment-id=\"43561\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/gopro-hampir-bangkrut-zero-hero-back-zero/attachment/go5/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/go5.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\" Design juga